<p>In this session we will complete the setup for the membrane protein KcsA and we will analyse the configuration files to perform the simulation<sup id="fnref:1" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote">1</a></sup>.</p>

<p>The updated files you need are available <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DA6XUkxuyqmfOWhCmT7IYZ9UO6Wv-FgH/view?usp=sharing">here</a>.
The archive contains the latest system we obtained last time (with
CHARMm 36 :|) and the configuration files.</p>

